# Git / GitHub

When committing or pushing this project, always use:

- **Remote:** `https://github.com/laegoIas/Viewership_model.git`
- **Branch:** `main`
- **Push command:** `py scripts/push.py` (after committing)

If `origin` points elsewhere, reset it before pushing:

```bash
git remote set-url origin https://github.com/laegoIas/Viewership_model.git
git push -u origin main
```
